article_title: Max Wise ousts incumbent Sara Beth Gregory in Kentucky's 16th Senate district
article_text: In one of the hottest statehouse races, Republicans in south-central Kentucky's 16th Senate district ousted incumbent Sara Beth Gregory of Monticello.
